WEBVTT

00:00:04.880 --> 00:00:10.052
Is the destiny of mankind controlled
by some transcendental entity or Law?

00:00:10.928 --> 00:00:14.056
Is it like the hand of
God hovering above?

00:00:15.057 --> 00:00:16.892
At least it is true...

00:00:17.351 --> 00:00:21.022
...that man has no
control, even over his own will.

00:00:25.026 --> 00:00:29.864
It is my perception that a true
friend never relies on another's dream.

00:00:30.656 --> 00:00:32.575
A person with the potential...

00:00:33.159 --> 00:00:36.912
...to be my true friend must be able to
find his reason for life without my help.

00:00:38.039 --> 00:00:44.587
And, he would have to put his heart
and soul into protecting his dream.

00:00:45.296 --> 00:00:48.215
He would never hesitate to
fight for his dream, even against me.

00:00:50.426 --> 00:00:52.344
For me, a true friend is...

00:00:53.721 --> 00:00:56.849
...one who stands
equal on those terms.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:04.074
